{
  "chapters": [
    {
      "id": "chapter3",
      "title": "The Idea Sprint",
      "background": "your_room_afternoon.jpg",
      "music": "lofi_soft.mp3",
      "events": [
        {
          "id": "scene1",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You’ve been thinking about what Aira said yesterday. Hackathons aren’t about perfection — they’re about possibility. You open your laptop."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Alright, Aira. I’ve got my courage. I’ve got my imaginary team. Now what? How do I actually… make an idea?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "grinning",
              "text": "Ah, the million-dollar question — where do ideas come from? Today, my curious friend, you’re about to find out."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene2",
          "background": "idea_chamber.jpg",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Like clockwork, you find yourself back in cyberspace. Surrounding you are floating notes and pictures connected by glowing cyan strings."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Welcome to the Idea Sprint Chamber! Every hacker’s imagination starts here. Think of it like a brainstorming dojo — no overthinking allowed."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "thinking",
              "text": "Wait… no overthinking? That’s a rather hard ask for someone like me."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "grinning",
              "text": "Exactly. The biggest mistake beginners make is overthinking. Hackathons are fast. You create first, refine later."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "teaching",
              "text": "Every great idea starts with three questions: 1️⃣ What problem do I want to solve? 2️⃣ Who am I helping? 3️⃣ How can technology make it better?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "teaching",
              "text": "Time to brainstorm! Devpost challenges often ask for real-world solutions. Focus on a problem, the user, and a technological solution."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene3",
          "type": "choice",
          "prompt": "What kind of challenge excites you the most?",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "Helping the environment",
              "nextScene": "scene3_env"
            },
            {
              "text": "Improving education",
              "nextScene": "scene3_edu"
            },
            {
              "text": "Supporting mental health",
              "nextScene": "scene3_health"
            },
            {
              "text": "Making technology more accessible",
              "nextScene": "scene3_access"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene3_env",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Eco-innovator detected! Sustainability challenges are huge at hackathons — from waste reduction to renewable energy apps. A noble cause, and technology can help make it happen."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene3_edu",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "A learning enthusiast! EdTech is one of the hottest hackathon categories. Projects that make learning fun and accessible can really stand out."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene3_health",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "Heart-driven hacker! Mental health innovations can truly change lives — from mindfulness apps to supportive communities. It’s about small steps that help others grow."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene3_access",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "grinning",
              "text": "Tech for all — I like it! Accessibility projects make digital spaces inclusive. Whether for young or old, improving access always matters."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene4",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "teaching",
              "text": "Nice! That’s your theme seed. Every big project starts with just one spark. Now, let’s take it further."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Aira waves her hand — the panels merge into a glowing holographic mind map resembling a chalkboard in cyberspace."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Imagine this formula: Problem + Technology + Impact = Idea. Think of it like a recipe. Let’s cook up some innovation!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene5",
          "title": "Idea Builder MiniGame",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "After minutes of brainstorming, you lie down on a cold data floor, frustrated. Everything feels done before."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "tired",
              "text": "Ugh… I can’t think of anything new! Everything’s already been done."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "That’s a myth. Innovation doesn’t always mean new. Sometimes it means better, simpler, or more human. Small ideas can make big differences."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Look — one team built an app to track food donations. Another helped students find mentors. Simple ideas. Big impact."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "determined",
              "text": "Okay… I think I’m ready to try this brainstorming thing."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "grinning",
              "text": "Perfect! Because here comes your next challenge."
            }
          ],
          "minigame": {
            "minigame_type": "IdeaBuilderMiniGame",
            "minigame_title": "SDG Impact Builder — Scenario Solver",
            "builds": [
              {
                "id": 1,
                "scenario": "People want new shoes but aren't sure where to buy them.",
                "problem": {
                  "options": [
                    "People don't know where to look",
                    "Shoe stores are closed",
                    "Designers dislike sneakers"
                  ],
                  "correct": "People don't know where to look"
                },
                "solution": {
                  "options": [
                    "Create a curated store list",
                    "Build a new shoe prototype",
                    "Rewrite the app's backend"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Create a curated store list"
                },
                "sdg": {
                  "options": [
                    "SDG 8: Decent Work and Economic Growth",
                    "SDG 13: Climate Action",
                    "SDG 4: Quality Education"
                  ],
                  "correct": "SDG 8: Decent Work and Economic Growth",
                  "hint": "Which goal supports local businesses and consumer access?"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": 2,
                "scenario": "A community is unable to access fresh produce after a storm.",
                "problem": {
                  "options": [
                    "Bad weather blocking deliveries",
                    "Lack of designers",
                    "Too many shoes"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Bad weather blocking deliveries"
                },
                "solution": {
                  "options": [
                    "Set up temporary market stalls",
                    "Hire a presenter",
                    "Redesign the logo"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Set up temporary market stalls"
                },
                "sdg": {
                  "options": [
                    "SDG 2: Zero Hunger",
                    "SDG 7: Affordable and Clean Energy",
                    "SDG 16: Peace and Justice"
                  ],
                  "correct": "SDG 2: Zero Hunger",
                  "hint": "Which goal addresses food security and access?"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": 3,
                "scenario": "Users are confused by the app navigation and leave quickly.",
                "problem": {
                  "options": [
                    "Navigation is unclear",
                    "Servers are too fast",
                    "The pitch is too long"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Navigation is unclear"
                },
                "solution": {
                  "options": [
                    "Add clear user-flow hints",
                    "Increase server CPU",
                    "Write a long pitch script"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Add clear user-flow hints"
                },
                "sdg": {
                  "options": [
                    "SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure",
                    "SDG 14: Life Below Water",
                    "SDG 15: Life on Land"
                  ],
                  "correct": "SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure",
                  "hint": "Which goal promotes accessible technology and innovation?"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": 4,
                "scenario": "The team needs users to test their prototype this weekend.",
                "problem": {
                  "options": [
                    "No testers available",
                    "Design trend is outdated",
                    "Coffee is too hot"
                  ],
                  "correct": "No testers available"
                },
                "solution": {
                  "options": [
                    "Run a weekend testing pop-up",
                    "Change the color palette",
                    "Refactor CSS only"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Run a weekend testing pop-up"
                },
                "sdg": {
                  "options": [
                    "SDG 17: Partnerships for the Goals",
                    "SDG 6: Clean Water and Sanitation",
                    "SDG 11: Sustainable Cities"
                  ],
                  "correct": "SDG 17: Partnerships for the Goals",
                  "hint": "Which goal emphasizes collaboration and community engagement?"
                }
              },
              {
                "id": 5,
                "scenario": "The team wants to get press attention for their app launch.",
                "problem": {
                  "options": [
                    "No media contacts",
                    "Prototype has too many features",
                    "Servers are down"
                  ],
                  "correct": "No media contacts"
                },
                "solution": {
                  "options": [
                    "Prepare a press kit and outreach list",
                    "Add more animations",
                    "Encrypt the database"
                  ],
                  "correct": "Prepare a press kit and outreach list"
                },
                "sdg": {
                  "options": [
                    "SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure",
                    "SDG 3: Good Health and Well-being",
                    "SDG 12: Responsible Consumption"
                  ],
                  "correct": "SDG 9: Industry, Innovation and Infrastructure",
                  "hint": "Which goal supports innovation awareness and technology advancement?"
                }
              }
            ],
            "completion_message": "You matched problems, solutions and SDGs like a pro — mission complete!",
            "achievement": {
              "title": "SDG Scenario Master",
              "description": "Perfectly matched all problem-solution-SDG scenarios",
              "badge": "🎯🌍"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "scene7",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "clapping",
              "text": "Fantastic! See? You brainstormed like a real innovator — fast, focused, and fearless."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "That was actually kinda fun. I didn’t realize ideas could form that easily when you just… try."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "That’s the hackathon magic — creativity under time pressure. You don’t wait for inspiration. You build it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene8",
          "type": "choice",
          "prompt": "How do you feel about your idea?",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text": "Proud! It’s something I’d love to build.",
              "nextScene": "scene8_proud"
            },
            {
              "text": "Curious — I want to explore it more.",
              "nextScene": "scene8_curious"
            },
            {
              "text": "Unsure. It still feels rough.",
              "nextScene": "scene8_unsure"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene8_proud",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "Confidence! The first step to innovation is believing your idea matters. Nobody can believe in your vision more than you do."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene8_curious",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Curiosity is your compass. Keep exploring — even rough edges lead to brilliance. Every twist gives you something new."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene8_unsure",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "Every great idea starts rough. The first draft isn’t supposed to be perfect — it’s supposed to exist. Believe it’s worth pursuing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene9",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "You’ve completed your third quest!"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "proud",
              "text": "Not bad for someone who almost ignored that hackathon email!"
            }
          ],
          "completion_message": "Completed Chpater 3",
          "achievement": {
          "title": "Innovation Spark",
          "description": "Complete Chapter 3 of How to Hackathon",
          "reward_points": 10,
          "icon": "chapter3complete.png"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "scene10",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Your Discord pings: “The Byteon Hackathon officially starts NOW!” Opening Ceremony Live!"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "A countdown timer appears in the corner of your screen. 48:00:00 remaining"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "determined",
              "text": "This is it… it’s actually starting."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "happy",
              "text": "From this moment forward — everything you build counts!"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "The screen shifts to a livestream window. Organizers speak, The theme is revealed, submission criteria clarified, mentors are introduced."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Chat floods with messages"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "“Good luck everyone!”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "“Let’s gooo!”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "“Team CultureQuest ready!”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "Pay attention. The judging criteria tells you what to prioritize."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "A floating checklist appears: Innovation, Impact, Technical Implementation, Presentation"
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "thinking",
              "text": "So it’s not just about coding something flashy…"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "clapping",
              "text": "Exactly. It’s about solving the problem well."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene11",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Your team jumps into a Discord voice channel. Cameras on. Slight chaos."
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Okay. We need a Minimum Viable Product (MVP)."
            },
            {
              "character": "Luna",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "I’ll start designing wireframes right now."
            },
            {
              "character": "Maya",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "I’ll refine the problem statement and SDG alignment for the submission page."
            },
            {
              "character": "Maya",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "What should we prioritize first?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Aira summons a Kanban board again."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "teaching",
              "text": "Rule of hackathons: Build the core feature first. Fancy extras come later."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "teaching",
              "text": "Build the backbone. Decorate later."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "A couple of hours later"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "The timer reads: 36:12:44 remaining"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Suddenly—"
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Uh… guys? The login system isn’t connecting to the database."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "..."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "thinking",
              "text": "Is that… bad?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Very."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Error messages flashes red. Aira appears calmly."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "grinning",
              "text": "Congratulations. You’ve unlocked your first bug."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "tired",
              "text": "That’s not funny."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Hackathons aren’t defined by smooth builds. They’re defined by recovery."
            }
            ],
              "minigame": {
              "minigame_type":"MultipleChoice",
              "minigame_title": "Bug Response",
              "description": "Aira (voice-over): Drag and drop each role to the task. Choose the best response:",
               "tasks": [
                {
                  "id": 1,
                  "task": "What do you when there is a bug?",
                  "options": ["Panic", "Scrap everything", "Debug step-by-step"],
                  "correct_answer": ["Debug step-by-step"]
                },
                {
                  "id": 2,
                  "task": "Which technique helps you find errors by going through the code step by step?",
                  "options": ["Guessing solutions", "Debug step-by-step", "Skipping tests"],
                  "correct_answer": ["Debug step-by-step"]
                },
                {
                  "id": 3,
                  "task": "Which of the following is *not* a common debugging action?",
                  "options": ["Check error messages", "Change random lines", "Test after fixes"],
                  "correct_answer": ["Change random lines"]
                },
                {
                "id": 4,
                "task": "What is the first step in debugging a code issue?",
                "options": ["Run the code without looking", "Identify and understand the problem", "Ask someone else to do it"],
                "correct_answer": ["Identify and understand the problem"]
                },
                {
                  "id": 5,
                  "task": "What does debugging typically involve in programming?",
                  "options": ["Coding without errors", "Improving performance", "Finding and resolving bugs", "Designing new features"],
                  "correct_answer": ["Finding and resolving bugs"]
                }
              ],
              "dialogue": [
              {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Kenji shares screen. You help test inputs. After 20 tense minutes—"
              },
              {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "It’s fixed!"
              },
              {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Everyone cheers."
              }
              ]
            }
        },
        {
          "id": "scene12",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Discord announcement: Workshop Starting: “Rapid Prototyping with APIs” Live in #workshops"
            },
            {
              "character": "Maya",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Should we watch it?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "We’re kind of busy…"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Strategic learning can save hours."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You open the workshop stream in a split screen. A mentor demonstrates a faster way to integrate authentication."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Kenji pauses."
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Wait… that’s way cleaner than what I’m doing."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Sometimes, stopping to learn speeds you up."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "scene13",
          "dialogs": [
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Time passes."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Timer: 18:05:11 remaining. Your eyes burn. Empty mug beside you."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "Hydration and rest improve performance."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "tired",
              "text": "Are you telling me to touch grass?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "gentle",
              "text": "I’m telling you to stretch."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You grab coffee. Luna laughs about sleep deprivation. Kenji finally smiles. Maya shares memes in team chat."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Even during pressure — laughter happens. Core feature works. Now the team debates."
            },
            {
              "character": "Luna",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Should we add progress tracking?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "We have time for one extra feature."
            },
            {
              "character": "Maya",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "If it strengthens impact, it’s worth it."
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Impact clarity wins over decoration."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Couple of hours pass."
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Discord pings: Midpoint submission reminder: 12 hours left"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You upload screenshots for feedback. A mentor comments: “Strong concept. Clarify user journey.”"
            },
            {
              "character": "Luna",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "I’ll improve onboarding screens."
            },
            {
              "character": "Kenji",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "I’ll clean up the code for demo stability."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "determined",
              "text": "We’re actually doing this…"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "Timer: 03:14:32 remaining"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Now it’s time to prepare for the big stage — The Pitch!"
            },
            {
              "character": "Narrator",
              "pose": "neutral",
              "text": "You have an idea on what comes up next now. You ask with the confidence of someone curious."
            },
            {
              "character": "You",
              "pose": "thinking",
              "text": "The pitch?"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Exactly! we’ll craft your voice, your story, and your confidence. Because every great idea deserves to be heard!"
            },
            {
              "character": "Aira",
              "pose": "smiling",
              "text": "Rest for a bit then we will record a video for the pitch."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
